# Acknowledgments

This project was developed for the **Data Mining and Text Analytics** course at **IULM University** (A.A. 2025 – 2026), taught by **Dr. Alessandro Bruno**.

## Tools & Libraries Used
- **Google Gemini**: For advanced multimodal text extraction and analysis.
- **Streamlit**: For building the interactive web dashboard.
- **Pydantic**: For data validation and structured output parsing.
- **Generative AI Tools**: Code debugging and scaffolding assistance provided by AI agents.

## Credits & Inspiration
- The project structure is inspired by modern ESG reporting standards (ESRS, GRI).
- Design aesthetics are inspired by professional corporate dashboards (e.g. Ferrero Sustainability Reports).
- Thanks to the open-source community for the Python libraries used in this project.

